
    flowchart TD
        %% Define styles
        classDef reporting fill:#f99,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;
        classDef db fill:#9ff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;

        %% Reporting System
        A[Reporting System]:::reporting --> B[Generate KFMS Plot]
        A --> C[Create PDF Report]
